# Job Tracker — environment variables
#
# This app is a fully client-side, static SPA. All data lives in the browser's
# localStorage, so NO environment variables are required to run, build, or deploy it.
#
# This file exists as a template for forks that add a backend or third-party
# services. Copy it to `.env` and fill in real values — `.env` is gitignored and
# must never be committed.
#
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_ to client code. Example:
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.example.com
# VITE_ANALYTICS_ID=your-analytics-id-here
